text.tspan: After the research and rounds of discussion with data, b2c team and develop teams, I organized the requirements
Target User is 40-45 Male, premium brand.
Experteer logo remain in the same typographic style and colour (no modifications)
The Beyond Jobs logo use an analogy of a career path, career growth, career success, satisfaction, salary, fast track
Beyond Jobs utilises Artificial Intelligence to predict your career path (personalised career paths)
The Beyond Jobs logo needs to be working in conjunction with the Experteer logo (sit underneath, next to it, ...)
Another idea was to use the arrow in conjunction with a path (start point - next / end point) sort of a line connecting
two points (as this would stand for the career path)
